      section
        h2 Recursion
        h3 A function that calls itself is called **recursive**
        pre
          code.language-javascript.
            function power(base, exponent) {
            if (exponent == 0)
              return 1;
            else
              return base * power(base, exponent - 1);
            }

            console.log(power(2, 3));
            // → 8
      
